OL,4,CSomerset reservoir levels among lowest
OL,5,Cin UK
OL,7,FBristol Water operates each of those
OL,8,Fmajor reservoirs. As of 1 August, the
OL,9,Ftotal reservoir storage for the
OL,10,Fsupplier's area was at 50%. On the
OL,11,Fsame date in 2024, storage was at 73%.
OL,13,FThe latest checks revealed that Chew
OL,14,FValley Lake, Cheddar Reservoir and
OL,15,FBlagdon Lake have all dropped below
OL,16,Fhalf-full, falling to 49%, 41% and 47%
OL,17,F- down from 78%, 59% and 77% last year.
