OL,5,Cin UK
OL,7,FThe Director of Drinking Water
OL,8,FServices at Bristol Water Richard
OL,9,FStanbrook is encouraging people in the
OL,10,Fregion to use water-saving methods
OL,11,Flike taking short showers, turning the
OL,12,Ftap off when brushing teeth, and
OL,13,Freusing water to water gardens.
OL,15,FHe said: "All these small things go a
OL,16,Flong way to help us to conserve this
OL,17,Freally precious resource."
OL,19,FHowever, he also sought to reassure
OL,20,Fcustomers.
