OL,4,CSomerset reservoir levels among lowest
OL,5,Cin UK
OL,7,FHe explained: "This is part of our
OL,8,Fplanned use of our water. We build
OL,9,Fthese reservoirs up during the winter
OL,10,Fand draw down on them in the summer."
OL,12,FHe added: "We are using our water
OL,13,Fwisely, we know our customers are
OL,14,Fusing it wisely.
OL,16,F"We supply 300 million litres a day to
OL,17,Fcustomers, over 1.2 million customers
OL,18,F,and that has grown in the summer by
OL,19,F10 per cent. We're also seeing
OL,20,Fdomestic use grow as more people come
OL,21,Fto Bristol."
