OL,7,FExperts warn climate change is driving
OL,8,Fmore extreme weather conditions in the
OL,9,FUK, worsening drought and dry spells,
OL,10,Fand making heatwaves more frequent and
OL,11,Fsevere.
OL,13,FDespite unsettled weather in July with
OL,14,Fmany places seeing heavy rain or
OL,15,Fshowers, it was still the fifth
OL,16,Fwarmest on record.
